Feature:Update project

  Background: set connection to pivotal tracker API REST
    Given I have set a connection to pivotal tracker API service
    And I have the next parameters to create a project:

      | name   | project to update |
      | public | true              |
    And I have the /projects endpoint
    And I sent a project POST request
    And stored as Project1

  @project
  Scenario: Update name of project
    Given I have a project created
    And I have project updated as a new project name
    When I send a project PUT request to /projects/[Project1.id] endpoint
    Then I expect the status code 200
    And The project name should be equal to project updated
